432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"別人垂手可得嘅嘢丶但我要出九牛二虎之力先勉強擁有丶而且係無選擇之下嘅替代品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2bc5fe022018492fabb2a1040962e8e0c83467","tid":2306881,"uid":15753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"一出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcde373715857ada77cb0e6ccf7d3b71220e752","tid":2306881,"uid":224190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"f34f201848497d78f526583489e62a5dab8df12d","tid":2306881,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ef2f7f94d9e9a02bc5c3f26675d6a064f5f62c9","tid":2306881,"uid":56432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"別人垂手可得嘅嘢丶但我要出九牛二虎之力先勉強擁有丶而且係無選擇之下嘅替代品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"A challenge and an experience <br />\nGood for you"},{"pid":"ce01a12cdbc4679685db096cd94db2d7bbc544b7","tid":2306881,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"我們從以前開始，就理應一直是被如此教導的。<br />\n<br />\n就算不直接地用語言說出來，看到包圍着我們的這個世界就應該能夠明白吧？<br />\n<br />\n因為電視呀網絡呀新聞裏所傳達的&ldquo;滿溢着希望的信息&rdquo;就是這樣說的嘛。<br />\n<br />\n「贏不了的人，不努力的人，就算努力也贏不了的人，都等同於無價值的垃圾。」<br />\n<br />\n有價值的人類和無價值的人類從出生的那一瞬就已經被明確地區分開了 。<br />\n無能的人類就算再怎麼努力，都無法成為有價值的人類。<br />\n<br />\n小型犬不管再怎麼努力，都無法成為大型犬；而企鵝努力再怎麼努力，都無法飛上天空。即是說，所謂無能的人類，就是不管做什麼都是無用的。有能的人類不是去成為的，而是從出生的那一刻起就擁有了所謂的才能。"},{"pid":"b3bc324e9a416a6e392c0270b6c4332f1b798ccf","tid":2306881,"uid":60451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"公開試炒撚晒, 搵唔到工 ,溝唔到女<br />\n每一次都係令自己更失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf32f1642040da0b6bfd655bc3bb0f4977b857be","tid":2306881,"uid":71849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"大學畢業+開始返工<br />\n發覺原來自己好廢<br />\n做野好慢<br />\n以為自己抗壓能力好好<br />\n原來日日比人屌<br />\n自己真係愈黎愈depress"}]}